    			<hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>-y-ōṭ·ṭai <hi rend="grantha">sāmānya</hi>m al·lātatu vilaikku koṇ·ṭō<unclear>m e</unclear>
    			<lb break="no" n="5"/>ṉ·ṟu tāmum· <hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>n=tatiyum· vi<hi rend="grantha">śe<unclear>ṣa</unclear>m</hi> <hi rend="grantha">anubha</hi>vik·ka perāt<unclear>ā</unclear>rāṉār
    		</p>
